Gemma Merna https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gemma_Merna 0 Gemma Merna (born 6 February 1984) is an English actress, model and yoga teacher. She is best known for portraying the role of Carmel McQueen in the Channel 4 soap opera Hollyoaks from 2006 to 2014.
